title: Silent Hill 4: The Room playthrough ‚Äî Part 2
description: The beginning of this part is pretty bad. Had technical difficulties beforehand, plus I died a few times and had to redo some stuff. But after that, the game started to grow on me. The story started to unravel and I started getting used to the controls. Now I'm enjoying the game quite a bit. I think it's really creepy, and it definitely spooped me hard a couple times.
